data.description: This beautiful ranch is nestled in a peaceful and quiet Stone Mountain neighborhood. The traditional floor plan features a warm and welcoming interior and contains good-sized living spaces. The rooms are a good size making it a great  home for a small family. The adjoining bathroom boasts a walk-in shower and tile flooring. Adding to the home's appeal are light colored LVP floors throughout. Unwind or entertain in the beautifully maintained backyard that comes complete with a large patio and built in fire pit. A place where wonderful memories are made. Featuring just the suburban atmosphere you are looking for. This beautiful home is 8 minutes from Stone Mountain park and has great shopping and restaurants only minutes away. This unique home won't last long. Want to know more? Call today!
